The paper deals with the ambiguity function of a MIMO radar system, which involves signal processing, information theory, and communication theory. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) is the most likely category. The paper also involves radar system design and optimization, which falls under cs.SI (Systems and Control). The paper deals with signal processing and system modeling, which are relevant to cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper involves the use of radio frequency (RF) signals, which is relevant to cs.RF (Networking and Internet Architecture). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of the performance of the MIMO radar system, which falls under cs.SP (Signal Processing).
